r: @robertwb (since we discussed this together)
cc: @aaltay @charlesccychen @bjchambers 

This PR does the following:
* Refactor `MetricsEnvironment` to use a per-thread stack instead of a single variable. This is to allow for easy access without `threading.local` overhead.
* Cythonize the `ScopedMetricsContainer` so that a context switch is a simple list append, instead of having to go through `threading.local`.
* Make `DoFnRunner` do the metrics context switch, just like the logging context switch (we use `ScopedMetricsContainer`) - every runner will get this with the SDK.
